nl.naturalis.nda.domain

Class Expert

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.naturalis.nda.domain.NdaDomainObject
      • nl.naturalis.nda.domain.Agent
        • nl.naturalis.nda.domain.Person
          • nl.naturalis.nda.domain.Expert

  • public class Expert
extends Person
    An Expert represents a person or organization who is regarded as an authority with respect to a particular species. An expert is not to be confused with the person who first described and named a species (for whom the term "author" is reserved). Expert is a subclass Person even though it has no properties of its known. This is because for an Expert, his/her name may be unknown (null), which would be dubious for a regular Person. With an Expert either his/her name or his/her organization may be unknown as long as at least one is known.
